Package: spatialtestR
Type: Package
Title: Testing Helpers for Spatial Raster Functions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jule", "Pfeiffer",
    email = "pfeiffer.jule@proton.me",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides generator functions for synthetic terra SpatRaster
    test fixtures, testthat-compatible expect_*() assertions for checking
    structural properties (dimensions, CRS), value ranges, and robustness
    (NA consistency, absence of Inf values), and a diagnostic function
    (summarize_transformation()) that reports geometry, value statistics,
    and a linear-regression-based classification of how an input raster
    was transformed into an output raster.
